This product includes software developed by the MISAKA Foundation
(https://misaka.network/).

This product includes post-quantum cryptographic implementations based on:
- ML-DSA-65 (FIPS 204 / Dilithium3) via pqcrypto-dilithium
- ML-KEM-768 (FIPS 203 / Kyber768) via pqcrypto-kyber

This product includes consensus algorithms inspired by:
- Narwhal & Bullshark (Danezis et al., 2022)
- GhostDAG (Sompolinsky & Zohar, 2018)
- Kaspa (kaspanet.org) — architectural reference

Third-party dependencies are listed in Cargo.lock with their
respective licenses. Notable dependencies:
- RocksDB (Apache-2.0 / GPL-2.0)
- Anchor Framework (Apache-2.0)
- tokio (MIT)
- axum (MIT)
- blake3 (CC0-1.0 / Apache-2.0)
- sha3 (MIT / Apache-2.0)
